import { Box, Typography } from '@mui/material'
import React from 'react'

  return (
    <Box>
      <Box>
        <Typography variant='h6'>Popular Health Checkup Packages</Typography>
      </Box>
      <Box sx={{display:'flex',flexDirection:'row'}}>

      </Box>
    </Box>
  )
}

export default SecondPage
